c。asso就邊間都有機上三大，<span style=\"color: red;\">但cccu acct要奶人袋底，做到隻狗先</span>得</blockquote><br />\n點解咁講？</blockquote><br />\n個prog leader要你係咁幫手做嘢，忙到嘔，仲要成日發脾氣叫人get out</blockquote><br />\n個個都要幫佢手做？</blockquote><br />\n圍內做個乜鬼committe先會</blockquote><br />\n咁唔參加個committee得唔得架<br />\n個課程本身係咪背野多？</blockquote><br />\n姐係呢 無入去做野都可以升既<br />\n同埋我唔識晒咁多人 <br />\n但我識果幾個 都真心想幫手做野<br />\n唔係你講到去做狗咁<br />\n自己覺得無能力handle當初就唔應該入soc"},{"pid":"7f5ecf7efd839de811d49846ae39d9a0b11931b5","tid":322014,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T17:21:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想知兩間分別係邊<br />\n讀既野有無咩唔同<br />\n而且想升返上三大acct有無可能？</blockquote><br />\nhkcc。asso就邊間都有機上三大，<span style=\"color: red;\">但cccu acct要奶人袋底，做到隻狗先</span>得</blockquote><br />\n點解咁講？</blockquote><br />\n個prog leader要你係咁幫手做嘢，忙到嘔，仲要成日發脾氣叫人get out</blockquote><br />\n個個都要幫佢手做？</blockquote><br />\n圍內做個乜鬼committe先會</blockquote><br />\n咁唔參加個committee得唔得架<br />\n個課程本身係咪背野多？</blockquote><br />\n你想入就入呀?<br />\n佢嗰個committee好多人爭架<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入之前又要畀啲yr2 interview<br />\n入到去又成日畀個prog leader+班yr2 撚 (乜尻都撚)<br />\n又要做到隻狗+join埋啲濕尻活動<br />\n好似3月咋嘛, 最凍嗰日叫人行早山喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過讀acct就間間都差唔多架啦<br />\n唻唻去去都係讀嗰啲架啦 (fa, ma/cost acct, blaw, audit, taxation)"},{"pid":"3f01dc224a12823024cc762c672bac2a94c94188","tid":322014,"uid":106798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T17:23:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>asso學生等於垃圾？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/293630/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/293630/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n有堆asshole仔喺呢個po度比純正大學生圍剿緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n作為asshole仔嘅你仲唔快啲過去增援?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgm